# MVP Boundaries

- In MVP, focus on Guitar Pro related structured sources, `MIDI`, `MusicXML`, manual text/tab-like inputs and a controlled screenshot path.
- Do not expand MVP into audio transcription, audio-first workflows, raw audio parsing, vocal workflow, or claims of full automatic accuracy; raw audio note extraction and audio-assisted verification remain out of scope.
- Produce editable scaffolds, warnings and review outputs, not final polished arrangements.
- Prefer explicit limitations and fallback paths over vague statements like "the AI should understand it."
